Detailed Description

cvmx_l2c_dut

L2C_DUT = L2C DUTAG Register

Description: L2C Duplicate Tag State Register

Notes: (1) When using the L2T, L2D or FINV Debug probe feature, an LDD command issued by the diagnostic PP WILL NOT update the DuTags. (2) L2T, L2D, FINV MUST BE mutually exclusive (only one enabled at a time). (3) Force Invalidate is intended as a means for SW to invalidate the L2 Cache while also writing back dirty data to memory to maintain coherency. (A side effect of FINV is that an LDD L2 fill is launched which fills data into the L2 DS).
